snippet.title: Fuuun Gokuu Ninden (JPN Psone) - Stage 1-1
snippet.description:
AKA Fuun Goku Ninden
Gameplay video of this Japan only 2D action platformer game for Playstation. As you can see the sound effects are a bit annoying. They get even worse with the Kappa character that I'll be showcasing in a future video.

The game itself is OK but I enjoy the ability to throw enemies. It's pretty basic overall.
